 (33,1,21,'','办理一级园复验与新申报的手续及注意事项','<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 37px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;\">办理一级园复验与新申报的手续及注意事项</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 37px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">根据上海市教育委员会沪教委基</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">[2002]69</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">《上海市教育委员会关于上海市托幼协会对本市一级幼儿园、托儿所资质进行审核的通知》、沪教委基</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">[2003]87</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">《上海市教育委员会关于进一步规范本市托幼园所办学等级评估办法的意见》的文件精神，对已取得办学等级三年以上的一级园（所）进行办学等级资格重新认定，（即需进行复验后再作认定是否符合一级园等级的标准）。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">复验园或新申报一级园申报过程中的手续及注意事项：</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">一、申报需交材料：（下列材料各交一份，需加盖公章）</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、申请报告</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、自评报告</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">、自评分</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">二、材料交送地点：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">上海市托幼协会：石门二路</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">199</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">弄</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">404</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">室（近北京西路）邮编：</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">200041</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">（同时网上发送至上海市教育评估院）</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">三、申报材料截止时间：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">上半年为</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">30</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">止，下半年为</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">9</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">30</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">止。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">四、按规定时间必须复验重新认定一级资格的园（所），如不申报，将作自动放弃，不得再按一级园收费。（如遇特殊情况需延期半年，必须以书面形式向上海市托幼协会提出申请，如要延期一年，必须向市教委基教处提出书面申请并加盖公章）。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; line-height: 37px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2012.3.1</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>','2018-08-22 10:32:05',1,-1,-1,-1,'2018-08-22 10:32:05',-1,'2018-08-22 10:32:05',-1,'ID',NULL,NULL,NULL);
